description: Calculates the percent variance between the header level Tax amount for this Supplier Invoice and its related Purchase Orders (s).

fieldName: MR Invoice and PO Header Level Tax Amount Variance
description: Calculates the amount variance between the header level tax field on this Supplier Invoice and related Purchase Order(s).

fieldName: MR Invoice has Lines that exceed Amount or Quantity Received
description:
Can be used in a match rule to detect if an invoice has lines that exceed amounts or quantities received.
This field is a Boolean to indicate if an invoice has lines that exceed amounts or quantities received.

fieldName: MR Invoice Line Retention Amount % Variance
description: The percent variance between Invoice Line Retention Amount and Extended Amount multiplied by Percent to Retain

fieldName: MR Invoice Line Retention Amount Variance
description: The amount variance between Invoice Line Retention Amount and Extended Amount multiplied by Percent to Retain

fieldName: MR Invoice Total and PO Total Amount % Variance
description: Calculates the percent variance between the Total Amount for this Supplier invoice and its related Purchase Order(s). This amount does not include any deductions such as withholding tax and retention.

fieldName: MR Invoice Total and PO Total Amount Variance
description: Calculates the amount variance between the Total Amount for this Supplier invoice and its related Purchase Order (s). Includes the following landed costs - tax, freight, other, for both Purchase Order and Supplier Invoice Amounts. This amount does not include any deductions such as withholding tax and retention.

fieldName: MR Invoice Total and PO Total Amount Variance Excluding Landed Costs
description: Calculates the amount variance between the Total Amount for this Supplier invoice and its related Purchase Order(s). Excludes the following landed costs - tax, freight, other, for both Purchase Order and Supplier Invoice Amounts. This amount does not include any deductions such as withholding tax and retention.

fieldName: MR Is Any Change Order Line Quantity Greater than PO Line Quantity
description: Returns true if any change order line quantity is greater than the PO line quantity.

fieldName: MR Max Invoice to PO Line Unit Cost Variance
description:
Can be used in a match rule to set an amount threshold or tolerance for invoice lines where the unit cost does not match the purchase order line unit cost.
This field compares for each line on the invoice the Unit Cost for each purchase order and invoice line and returns the maximum.

fieldName: MR Max Inv to PO Line Unit Cost Percentage Variance
description:
Can be used in a match rule to set a percent threshold or tolerance for invoice lines where the unit cost does not match the purchase order line unit cost.
This field compares the Unit Cost for each purchase order and invoice line for each line on the invoice and returns the maximum % variance.
The three-letter ISO currency code MRO.

fieldName: MR Percentage of Total Invoiced that exceeds Contract Amount (from Invoice)
description: Percentage that the Total Amount Invoiced exceeds the Supplier Contract Amount. Returns 0 if not fully invoiced yet. May also return 0 if the Supplier Invoice is not associated with a Supplier Contract. This amount does not include any deductions such as withholding tax and retention.

fieldName: MR Percentage of Total Invoiced that exceeds Contract Amount (from Invoice Line)
description: Percentage that the Total Amount Invoiced per Supplier Contract on Supplier invoice lines  exceeds Supplier Contract Amount.

fieldName: MR Percentage of Total Invoiced that exceeds Contract Line Amount (from Supplier Invoice Line)
description: Percentage that the Total Amount Invoiced exceeds the Supplier Contract Line Extended Amount. Returns 0 if not fully invoiced yet. May also return 0 if the Supplier Invoice Line is not associated with a Supplier Contract.

fieldName: MR Percentage of Total Ordered that exceeds Contract Line Amount (from Order Line)
description: Percentage that the Total Amount Ordered exceeds the Supplier Contract Line Extended Amount. Returns 0 if not fully ordered yet. May also return 0 if the Contract Type does not allow ordering by line, or if the Purchase Order Line is not associated with a Supplier Contract.

fieldName: MR Percentage of Total Received that exceeds Contract Line Amount (from Receipt Line)
description: Percentage that the Total Amount Received exceeds the Supplier Contract Line Extended Amount. Returns 0 if not fully received yet. May also return 0 if the Contract Type does not allow receiving by line.

fieldName: MR Percentage of Total Received that exceeds PO Line Amount (from Receipt Line)
description: Percentage that the Total Amount Received exceeds the Purchase Order Line Extended Amount. Returns 0 if not fully received yet.

fieldName: MR Receipt has any lines where Total Quantity or Amount Received greater than Supplier Contract Line Quantity or Amount
description: Receipt contains Receipt Lines where Total Quantity or Total Amount Received for the related Supplier Contract Line is greater than it Quantity or Amount.

fieldName: MR Receipt has any lines where Total Quantity Received greater than PO Quantity
description: Receipt contains Receipt Lines where Total Quantity Received for the related Purchase Order Line is greater than the Order Quantity.

fieldName: MR Receipt has Receipt Line Quantity or Amount greater than Supplier Contract Line Quantity or Amount
description: Receipt has lines where quantity or amount received for the line is greater than the quantity or amount on the related Supplier Contract Line.

fieldName: MR Receipt has Receipt Quantity greater than Order Quantity
description: Receipt contains Receipt Lines where the Quantity Received for the line is greater than the Order Quantity on the related Purchase Order Line.

fieldName: MR Receipt Quantity greater than PO Quantity for all Receipt Lines
description: Receipt Line Quantity for this receipt plus all other Receipt Line Quantities for related PO Line greater than Quantity on related PO Line.

fieldName: MR Receipt Quantity greater than PO Quantity for this Receipt Line
description: The Quantity Received for the Receipt Line is greater than the Order Quantity on the related Purchase Order Line.

fieldName: MR Receipt Quantity greater than Supplier Contract Line Quantity for all Receipt Lines
description: Receipt Line Quantity for this receipt plus all other Receipt Line Quantities for related Supplier Contract Item Line greater than Quantity on related Supplier Contract Item Line.

fieldName: MR Receipt Quantity greater than Supplier Contract Line Quantity for this Receipt Line
description: The Quantity Received for the Receipt Line is greater than the Order Quantity on the related Supplier Contract Line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / Gross Receipt Line Quantity % Variance
description: Calculates the Quantity % Variance of the related Gross (no Returns included) Receipts of the allocating Supplier Contract or Purchase Order Line for all related Supplier Invoice lines including the current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / Gross Receipt Line Quantity Variance
description: Calculates the Quantity Amount Variance of the related Gross (no Returns included) Receipts of the allocating Supplier Contract or Purchase Order Line for all related Supplier Invoice lines including the current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / PO Line Extended Amount % Variance
description: Calculates the % variance between the PO line extended amount field and sum of all related invoice line extended amount fields including the current Supplier Invoice Line instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / PO Line Extended Amount Variance
description: Calculates the amount variance between the Extended Amount on the PO line and the sum of Extended Amounts on all related Supplier Invoice lines including the current Supplier Invoice Line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / PO Line Gross Amount % Variance
description: Calculates the % variance between the PO line gross amount field and sum of all related invoice line gross amount fields including the current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / PO Line Gross Amount Variance
description: Calculates the amount variance between the PO line gross amount field and sum of all related invoice line gross amount fields including the current Supplier Invoice Line instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / PO Line Quantity % Variance
description: Calculates the Quantity Variance Percentage of the PO Line for this current Supplier Invoice Line instance to the sum of all invoiced quantity for the PO Line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / PO Line Quantity Variance
description: Calculates the Quantity Variance of the PO Line for this current Supplier Invoice Line instance to the sum of all invoiced quantity for the PO Line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice/ Receipt Line Amount % Variance
description: Calculates the exteded amount Variance Percentage of the related Receipts (less Returns) of the allocating Supplier Contract or Purchase Order Line for this current Supplier Invoice Line instance. It compares the sum of the receipt amount less any applicable returned amount to the sum of all invoiced extended amount for the allocating line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice/ Receipt Line Amount Variance
description: Calculates the extended amount Variance of the related Receipts (less Returns) of the allocating Supplier Contract or Purchase Order Line for this current Supplier Invoice Line instance. It compares the sum of the receipt amount less any applicable returned quantity to the sum of all invoiced extended amount for the allocating line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice/ Receipt Line Quantity % Variance
description: Calculates the Quantity Variance Percentage of the related Receipts (less Returns) of the allocating Supplier Contract or Purchase Order Line for this current Supplier Invoice Line instance.  It compares the sum of the receipt quantity less any applicable returned quantity to the sum of all invoiced quantity for the allocating line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice/ Receipt Line Quantity Variance
description: Calculates the Quantity Variance of the related Receipts (less Returns) of the allocating Supplier Contract or Purchase Order Line for this current Supplier Invoice Line instance.  It compares the sum of the receipt quantity less any applicable returned quantity to the sum of all invoiced quantity for the allocating line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / Supplier Contract Line Quantity % Variance
description: Calculates the Quantity Percentage Variance of the allocating Supplier Contract Line for this current Supplier Invoice Line instance to the sum of all invoiced quantity for the Supplier Contract Line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice / Supplier Contract Line Quantity Variance
description: Calculates the Quantity Variance of the Supplier Contract Line for this current Supplier Invoice Line instance to the sum of all invoiced quantity for the Supplier Contract Line.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice and PO Header Level Freight Amount % Variance
description: Calculates the % variance between the PO header level freight field and sum of all related invoice header freight fields including current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice and PO Header Level Freight Amount Variance
description: Calculates the amount variance between the PO header level freight field and sum of all related invoice header freight fields including current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice and PO Header Level Other Charges Amount % Variance
description: Calculates the % variance between the PO header level other charges field and sum of all related invoice header other charges fields including current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice and PO Header Level Other Charges Amount Variance
description: Calculates the amount variance between the PO header level other charges field and sum of all related invoice header other charges fields including current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice and PO Header Level Tax  Amount % Variance
description: Calculates the % variance between the PO header level tax field and sum of all related invoice header tax fields including current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice and PO Header Level Tax Amount Variance
description: Calculates the amount variance between the PO header level tax field and sum of all related invoice header tax fields including current Supplier Invoice instance.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice Total and PO Total Amount % Variance
description: Calculates the % variance between the Total PO Amount field and sum of all related Total Invoice Amounts including current Supplier Invoice instance. This amount does not include any deductions such as withholding tax and retention.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice Total and PO Total Amount Variance
description: Calculates the amount variance between the Total PO Amount field and sum of all related Total Invoice Amounts including current Supplier Invoice instance. Includes the following landed costs - tax, freight, other for both Purchase Order and Supplier Invoice Amounts. Does not include Canceled or Draft Invoices. This amount does not include any deductions such as withholding tax and retention.

fieldName: MR Sum of Invoice Total and PO Total Amount Variance Excluding Landed Costs
description: Calculates the amount variance between the Sum of Total PO Amounts for purchase orders associated with the Invoice and sum of all related Total Invoice Amounts including current Supplier Invoice instance. Excludes the following landed costs - tax, freight, other for both Purchase Order and Supplier Invoice Amounts. Does not include Canceled or Draft Invoices. This amount does not include any deductions such as withholding tax and retention.

fieldName: MR SUM of Invoice Totals and PO Totals Percent Variance Excluding Landed Costs
description: Calculates the percent variance between the Total Amount of Supplier Invoices and their related Purchase Order(s). Excludes the following landed costs - tax, freight, other, for both Purchase Order and Supplier Invoice Amounts.

fieldName: MR Sum of Out of Balance Scheduled Amounts
description: The sum of Out of Balance scheduled amounts for contract lines on the Supplier Invoice or Purchase Order Schedule. Canceled contract lines are not included. A negative value means the total of contract line extended amounts is less than the total scheduled amount. If there are no installments the sum will equal the total of contract line extended amounts on the schedule.

description: Returns True if the Supplier Invoice Line has a related Contingent Worker Order Line.

fieldName: MR Supplier Invoice Line has Goods PO Line

fieldName: MR Supplier Invoice Line has PO Line

description: Returns true if the supplier event has the same default email address as an existing supplier.

fieldName: MR Total Invoice to PO Line Unit Cost Variance
description:
Can be used in a match rule to set a maximum amount threshold or tolerance for a unit cost variance for the entire invoice.
This field compares the Unit Cost for each purchase order and invoice line. It then sums the differences as a total.

fieldName: MR Total Non-PO Invoice Amount Percentage
description:
Can be used in a match rule to set a tolerance percentage for invoice lines that were not included on the purchase order.
This field adds up all invoice lines that were not included on the purchase order from which the invoice was created. It then divides by the total of all lines and multiplies by 100 to calculate a percentage.  Excludes Extended Amounts on Tax Only Invoices.

fieldName: MR Total of Non-PO Supplier Invoice Lines
description:
Can be used in a match rule to set an amount threshold or tolerance for invoice lines that were not referenced on the purchase order.
This field sums up the amount of all invoice lines that were not referenced on the purchase order from which the invoice was created.  Excludes Extended Amounts on Tax Only Invoices.

fieldName: MR Total Ordered Quantity of all related Goods Order Lines is greater than the Contract Line Quantity (from Order Line)
description: Goods Order Line Quantity for this Line plus all other Purchase Order Line Quantities for the related Supplier Contract Goods Line is greater than the Quantity on the related Supplier Contract Goods Line. Applicable only to Goods Lines. Service Order Lines without quantities will always return false.

fieldName: MR Worker having a name similar to the name on the Supplier Request exists
description: Can be used in a match rule to detect Supplier Requests where the name provided matches or is similar to an existing Worker.
